description: This work is a fantasy novel created by AI. It tells the story of a man who is transported to another world where swords and magic reign, and he, along with his companions, becomes embroiled in a battle against 'The Order of Evil'. It is an epic tale of intrigue, fateful encounters, and the adventures of the characters as they forge strong bonds. Character NFT's Ethereum Chain Sale: Characters from the novel have been transformed into non-fungible token (NFT). Each NFT features an original AI-generated design and unique character traits. These NFTs are now available for public sale on the Ethereum Chain for those interested.
name: ISEKAI AI Ordinals
